25°48'18 3"N 80°07’16.1"W
We have already seen tons of images taken from the sky, each one more magnificent than the other.
This is a combination of my passion for photography and art.
Sometimes the simplest landscape can create a beautiful scene when you take a moment to admire it from a different perspective.
